data.description: Discover unparalleled luxury living at 1266 Greenridge Avenue, a meticulously renovated European-inspired masterpiece in Lithonia, GA. Spanning over 7,000 square feet across three impeccable floors, this extraordinary residence combines timeless elegance with modern sophistication.    As you enter through the castle entry doors, you're greeted by the grandeur of Italian porcelain flooring and soaring 30-foot ceilings, complemented by European crown moldings and trim that exude refined charm. The glass staircase balustrades invite natural light to dance throughout the home, illuminating every exquisite detail.    Entertain with flair in the gourmet kitchen, featuring quartz countertops and high-end appliances, while the adjacent living spaces offer seamless flow for gatherings large and small. Indulge in cinematic experiences in the state-of-the-art home theater or unwind in the opulent master suite, boasting lavish amenities and serene vistas.    Outside, a palm tree-lined circle drive sets the stage for arrival, leading to the regal entrance. Step into the private oasis surrounded by lush greenery, where al fresco dining and relaxation await on the sprawling 1-acre estate. The neighborhood, renowned for its collection of breathtaking estates, offers exclusivity and prestige, ensuring an unparalleled lifestyle experience.    With its unparalleled craftsmanship, exquisite finishes, and meticulous attention to detail, 1266 Greenridge Avenue is more than just a home; it's a masterpiece of luxury living, awaiting its discerning new owner.
